  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Capable, Printable, ActorInterface
    public class Brachiosaur
extends Dinosaur
    Brachiosaur is a long neck herbivorous dinosaur which only eat fruits from trees. It's main actions will be handled in the playTurn method.
